The room was very cute with lots of charming details and although the interior was neither modern nor up to date it fitted the old property perfect and altogether the atmosphere was fantastic.	A week at this small but beautiful hotel, right in the heart of the fabullous Marais district, made our visit to Paris so memorable, The helpful and knowledgable Manager and the exquistely decorated rooms in 19th, century French style makes this place something special.	I did a lot of research before hand, as I was traveling with my 65 year Mum, and wanted her to have the comforts that not all European hotels have.